checkUpkeep(bytes).details: This is the function that the Chainlink nodes wil call to see if the lottery is ready to have a winner picked. The following should be true in oreder for upkeepNeeded to be true: 1. The time interval has passed between raffle runs 2. The lottery is open 3. The contract has ETH (has players) 4. Implicitly, your subcription has LINK

returns.upkeepNeeded: - true if it's time to restart the lottery
